    • findAllWohnungen

      public List<Wohnung> findAllWohnungen(String stringFilter)
      Service method to find all Wohnungen (apartments) based on a given string filter. If the filter string is null or empty, it returns all Wohnungen. If the filter string is provided, it first searches for all matching Adressen (addresses), extracts their IDs, and then finds all Wohnungen associated with those address IDs.
      Parameters:
      stringFilter - The filter string to search for matching Adressen. If null or empty, all Wohnungen are returned.
      Returns:
      A list of Wohnungen that match the given filter string. If no filter is provided, returns all Wohnungen.
